title: Chelsea Handler Interview and More
itunes:title: Chelsea Handler Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had Chelsea Handler call in where she spoke about her HBO special, her discussion she had with 50 cent supporting Trump and apologized for her comments she made earlier this week and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Pastor Daniel Chalmen for peeing on a woman, but you will definitely want to hear why he did it!
